  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13063764/switzerland_graubuenden-ski-region_arosa-lenzerheide_couple-enjoying-summit-view.jpg" alt="couplehero" data-udi="umb://media/0757b347e20e49108a66909b74edbe25" /></p>
<p>Ski holidays for romantic escapes - What better way to spend time with your partner than on a romantic week or <a data-udi="umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064" href="/{localLink:umb://document/52fab17731fa49639f8a0841e064a064}" title="Switzerland">weekend</a> away on a ski holiday - enjoy fine dining restaurants, stunning accommodation with spas and chair lifts made for two. </p>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;">
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><strong>Recommending:</strong> Luxury &amp; Spa Ski Holidays
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;">
<p><img src="/media/13050587/ski_spa.jpg" alt="spaski" data-udi="umb://media/15e8828839ab4a2e89830c0a0076f1a4" /></p>
<p>There is nothing more romantic then enjoying time together relaxing after a busy day on the slopes. See more on Michelin Star restaurants, Wellness &amp; Spa spaces and 5* luxury, high-quality  accommodation. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46}" class="c-btn">Luxury &amp; spa Skiing</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><strong>Recommending:</strong> All inclusive
<p><img src="/media/13103275/all-inclussive-option-566x377.jpg" alt="AllInclusive" data-udi="umb://media/9d650a8f6dc84a71b4ce3ee6c9f54126" /></p>
<p>Let the world take care of you as you put your feet up at the end of the day and together enjoy the life of all inclusive from food to drinks, swimming pools to saunas and king size beds to rooms with a view. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cdc6d10e4c8c4b42b12aa0b36e30ee30" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cdc6d10e4c8c4b42b12aa0b36e30ee30}" title="All Inclusive Ski Holidays" class="c-btn">All inclusive Skiing</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Our top rated couples resorts:</h2>
<p>We have selected a few resorts that reflect some key aspects when selecting a romantic ski holiday.</p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz, Switzerland</a></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">For a special occasion</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13095036/plate-of-food-resized.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/98e42f18fd0447169a236ef191429283" /></p>
<p>Romance means many things to many people, but a candle-lit dinner in a stunning setting usually encapsulates this.</p>
<p>For a truly special occasion and an escape like no other, treat yourselves to a fine-dining experience at a 2 star rated <a data-udi="umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b4c9b6c332ba475d8d2f9f940dba4d46}" title="Ski &amp; Spa Holidays">Michelin restaurant</a> in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a>. The <span>Da Vittorio is a wonderful setting for romance and some of the<a data-udi="umb://document/e9a3c77df19c4552878816499e7c956a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9a3c77df19c4552878816499e7c956a}" title="Insiders Guide: Where are the best ski resorts for foodies"> finest food</a> you will ever try. Meaning you can combine your love of skiing with your love of cuisine. </span></p>
<p><span>The combination of the cosy, warm restaurant paired with the absolutely amazing views of St Mortiz mountains as your back drop will certainly make any occasion special, making it the ideal place for anniversaries, birthdays, engagements or just quality time together.</span></p>
<p><span>St Moritz is an ideal ski location, with over 300km of slopes, overlooking a frozen lake.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" class="c-btn">View St Mortiz</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas, Lapland</a></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">The perfect escape</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13094856/glass-igloo-408x200.jpg" alt="glassigloo" data-udi="umb://media/c9ac7db735e1481780be668702287f2a" /></p>
<p>We must not forget the wonderous escape of Lapland and all that Finland has to offer - View of our <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland holidays</a>. </p>
<p>To book the perfect getaway, you want the combination of great skiing, relaxing evenings, and romantic nights. What better way then to wow your partner, than by booking a night in either our <a data-udi="umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145}" title="Northern Lights Adventures">Glass Igloos or Aurora Cabins</a> for a bed under the stars. </p>
<p>Gaze through your glass roofed accommodation at he unrivalled arctic night sky and be sure to catch a glimpse of the magical northern lights. Additionally, you can add on other excursions - such as a romantic <a data-udi="umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719" href="/{localLink:umb://document/588530ae17cd46a6ad7121ad9991d719}" title="Reindeer Rides">reindeer sleigh ride</a> for 2 or visiting the <a data-udi="umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e9d443cb665d4899b74aa61005c34869}" title="Ice Activities">Ice Hotel</a> for a unique experience. </p>
<p>Skiing in <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a> offers <a data-udi="umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a4a479e8266449e18b6b9e98eafdfcb0}" title="Lapland Holidays">Lapland</a> (Finland's) longest ski slopes with wide open runs surrounded by forests, as well as vast <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">cross-country</a> options. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" class="c-btn">View Yllas</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">Zell am See, Austria</a></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Quality time together</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13048528/_mg_5422.jpg" alt="hotelspa" data-udi="umb://media/05958a8826104977a654b288df7f4182" /></p>
<p>As a couple, finding quality time together to relax and be in each others company can be hard in todays busy, modern life. We recommend unwinding together at the <a data-udi="umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73}" title="Romantik Hotel"><span>Romantik Hotel Spa. </span></a></p>
<p><span>This spa offers everything you could possibly hope for - an interconnecting indoor/outdoor pool, adults only 'Emotion Spa', beauty and message treatments, sauna, whirlpool and steam room. This historic, charming, central hotel offers all you need. </span></p>
<p><span>There is plenty of great skiing to be had in Zell am See as well, with its high altitude and 3 ski areas on one lift pass.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" class="c-btn">View Zell am See</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel">Courchevel, France</a></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Touch of elegance </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13082916/photoingfrcrw1402jan15.jpg" alt="hotairballoon" data-udi="umb://media/a7b214c3cf4146caac1d35ff68f107c0" /></p>
<p>There is nothing more romantic than feeling your whole holiday has a touch of elegance to it. You will see why the <a data-udi="umb://document/f4a24e4bba9645fc9d135e61ab7503f1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f4a24e4bba9645fc9d135e61ab7503f1}" title="Insiders Guide: Royal ski resorts">royal family</a> chose Courchevel for their <a data-udi="umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6a8b15733cdd470bb0d866187156d07d}" title="Ski Resorts">ski holidays</a>, known for its world class skiing, it caters for all levels.</p>
<p>When a resort offers not only 5* rated spas, hot air balloon rides at sunrise and sunset, and a selection of designer boutiques this certainly sets a precedent.</p>
<p>When you also are aware that this resort was home to Prince William and Prince Harry's early years of skiing, it only heightens the idea of elegance and the want to add it to your ski bucket list.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" class="c-btn">View Courchevel</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Best romantic accommodation:</h2>
<p>A selection of some of our favourite romantic accommodation options based on the resorts above. </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><span>Romantik Hotel</span></h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">Zel am See</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13057319/romantik-hotel-schweizerhof-grindelwald-bernese-oberland-switzerland-spa-jacuzzi.jpg" alt="zelamseehotel" data-udi="umb://media/3d42db1c78554572a4d4cdf5aa6e560a" /></p>
<p>The Romantik hotel is full of charm and warmth and is set in the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/623c1118097f4c169108c9bc931e0af1}" title="Zell am See">historic Zel am See</a>. The hotel itself dates back to the 15th century and therefore is full of traditional, attractive features. Upgrade to the Garden Suites for a full luxury experience, with your own private lounge area and balcony overlooking the town and mountains. Enjoy the peace in the adults only spa area. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73" href="/{localLink:umb://document/262d882e891b42a88e772cd0dc48ec73}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Glass Igloo &amp; Aurora Cabin</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13073432/muotka-aurora-cabin-3.jpg" alt="auroracabin" data-udi="umb://media/d544b74372ff436d9a6a187d06671132" /></p>
<p>These unique overnight stay options take you away from the crowds of everyday life and transport you to your own private haven. Equipped with all you need for a night under stars, including a <a data-udi="umb://document/9a05a35cb8d34ed5816618ba9aef347a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9a05a35cb8d34ed5816618ba9aef347a}" title="Where to see the Northern Lights this winter">northern lights</a> wake-up call so you don't miss the show. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9933a896cd594899ac7150e009590145}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Chalets du Forum</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9e7d0f01e7964af0b7ee7c501cb0e893}" title="Courchevel">Courchevel</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13076730/69109714.jpg" alt="chaletforum" data-udi="umb://media/e455936b0b7a4a3496a7fae87270a38d" /></p>
<p>These <a data-udi="umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1839b76c30ed4fa08d4b2056caa1b257}" title="Chalets">chalets</a> offer the perfect traditional décor, with an alpine feel and spacious accommodation. Close to the ski lifts and slopes, as well as to the idyllic resort centre for shops and restaurants. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/485c386f082b4e689bfbda36c9b287d0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/485c386f082b4e689bfbda36c9b287d0}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-6">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Hotel Monopol</h3>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc17fe79ccd1491a92608658d3af9d55}" title="St. Moritz">St Moritz</a></h3>
<p><img src="/media/13081500/skybar_2-min.jpg" alt="hotelmonopol" data-udi="umb://media/c2668325f60c4c3f806afdb4dedafd73" /></p>
<p>In the heart of the resort, where you walk out on to the streets lined with boutique shops, this fashionable hotel offers a roof top bar for pre-dinner drinks and fine-dining and is decorated with local art. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/990d57a643344020abc9d610d2715f84" href="/{localLink:umb://document/990d57a643344020abc9d610d2715f84}" class="c-btn">View accommodation</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<h2>FAQ's for couples skiing holidays</h2>
<p><strong>Do you offer all inclusive ski holidays for couples?</strong> - Yes of course, see our <a data-udi="umb://document/cdc6d10e4c8c4b42b12aa0b36e30ee30" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cdc6d10e4c8c4b42b12aa0b36e30ee30}" title="All Inclusive Ski Holidays">all inclusive ski holidays</a> page for some ideas. </p>
<p><strong>Do you offer skiing holidays on Valentines Day? </strong>We certainly do, use our search bar at the top of the page to find your perfect holiday. Also do read our <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/blog/ski/romantic-valentines-day-ski-holiday/" target="_blank" title="Valentines">Valentines Insider's Guide</a> on how to make it an extra special trip. </p>
<p><strong>How many nights would you recommend for a couples skiing trip?</strong> This of course is slightly down to personal preference. At Inghams, we offer either longer ski breaks (7 nights) across all our resorts or short ski breaks to <a data-udi="umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d137b11ca7414c7b817405b2fd7405b8}" title="Ski Weekends &amp; Short Breaks to Switzerland">Switzerland</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel with confidence </h2>
<p>When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png" alt="safehands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
<div class="c-card_content c-section u-margin-top u-margin-bottom u-margin-left u-margin-right">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to book your holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Travel, accommodation and transfers? We’ve got you covered. Book your holiday online or give us a call. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
